commit a70c5e3c1ca91a949ead8531221b9423d8c457e1
Author: Erich Owens <erich.owens@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Mar 12 19:17:06 2026 -0700

    feat: Port Daddy v3.7.0 'The Control Plane' release
    
    Integrated high-fidelity maritime design system and swarm primitives:
    - 🧊 3D Swarm Graph: Three.js based spatial visualization of agents and ports.
    - 📡 Unified Swarm Radio: Real-time SSE timeline merging infra logs and agent notes.
    - 📬 Wild West Hailing: Ad-hoc inbox messaging without registry enforcement.
    - 🚩 Maritime Language: Signal flags and radio voices for precise coordination.
    - 📊 Swarm Benchmarking: CLI tool to measure daemon latency and throughput.
    - 🐕 Watchdog: Auto-restart deadman switch for daemon health.
    - 🔐 Security Soundness: Initial roadmap for formal verification via ProVerif/F*.
    - 🎓 Academy Redesign: Refactored tutorials with zero 'naked HTML' and unified typography.
    - 🛠️ Fixed: DNS Host-header blocks, CORS origins, and SVG radius errors.
    - 🧹 Cleaned: Moved internal tracking to STRATEGY_private_gitignore/.

