-      <p>Access your dev services by hostname instead of port numbers. Map <code style="font-family: var(--font-mono); background: rgba(0,102,204,0.08); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; border: none;">myapp-api.local</code> to your running service with a single command.</p>
