-      <h1>Harbors</h1>
-      <p>Permission namespaces for multi-agent systems. Issue HMAC-signed capability tokens so agents can only touch what they're supposed to touch.</p>
-      <div class="meta">
-        <span class="meta-item">
-          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
