+      <h1>Your First 5 Minutes with Port Daddy</h1>
+      <p>Welcome to the end of <code style="font-family: var(--font-mono); background: rgba(0,102,204,0.08); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; border: none;">lsof -i :3000</code> diagnostics and port conflict nightmares.</p>
+      <div class="meta">
