+      <h1>pd spawn</h1>
+      <p>Launch Ollama, Claude, Aider, and Gemini agents from one command. Port Daddy coordination — sessions, heartbeats, notes, salvage — is auto-wired.</p>
+      <div class="meta">
+        <span class="meta-item">
+          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
