+      <h2 id="what-are-phases">What are session phases?</h2>
+
+      <p>Sessions have a lifecycle. Phases let agents communicate their current state -- to other agents, to humans watching the dashboard, and to the salvage system if something goes wrong.</p>
+
+      <p>Think of phases like status labels on a pull request: <em>In Review</em>, <em>Changes Requested</em>, <em>Merged</em>. They don't enforce anything. They're a shared signal that answers the question "where are you in your work right now?" without requiring a dedicated communication channel.</p>
+
+      <p>Phases also feed the salvage system. When an agent dies and another agent picks up its work, the phase tells the rescuer exactly where the previous agent stopped. An agent with phase <code>testing</code> died while running tests -- the rescuer knows to look at test output, not at the implementation.</p>
+
+      <h2 id="phases">The 6 Phases</h2>
+
+      <p>Sessions can be in one of six phases. They flow roughly left to right, with <code>abandoned</code> as an escape hatch from anywhere:</p>
+
+      <div class="phase-diagram">
+        <svg viewBox="0 0 620 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="width: 100%; max-width: 620px; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
+          <!-- Main flow boxes -->
+          <rect x="10" y="30" width="90" height="36" rx="6" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#2C2C31" stroke-width="1.5"/>
+          <text x="55" y="52" text-anchor="middle" fill="#E8E8EC" font-family="monospace" font-size="11">planning</text>
+
+          <rect x="130" y="30" width="90" height="36" rx="6" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#2C2C31" stroke-width="1.5"/>
+          <text x="175" y="52" text-anchor="middle" fill="#E8E8EC" font-family="monospace" font-size="11">in_progress</text>
+
+          <rect x="250" y="30" width="90" height="36" rx="6" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#2C2C31" stroke-width="1.5"/>
+          <text x="295" y="52" text-anchor="middle" fill="#E8E8EC" font-family="monospace" font-size="11">testing</text>
+
+          <rect x="370" y="30" width="90" height="36" rx="6" fill="#1C1C1F" stroke="#2C2C31" stroke-width="1.5"/>
+          <text x="415" y="52" text-anchor="middle" fill="#E8E8EC" font-family="monospace" font-size="11">reviewing</text>
+
+          <rect x="490" y="30" width="90" height="36" rx="6" fill="#18794E" stroke="#18794E" stroke-width="1.5"/>
+          <text x="535" y="52" text-anchor="middle" fill="#fff" font-family="monospace" font-size="11">completed</text>
+
+          <!-- Arrows between main phases -->
+          <line x1="100" y1="48" x2="128" y2="48" stroke="#6B6B76" stroke-width="1.5" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
