+      <h1>Sugar Commands</h1>
+      <p>One-line agent lifecycle with <code style="font-family: var(--font-mono); background: rgba(0,102,204,0.08); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; border: none;">begin</code>, <code style="font-family: var(--font-mono); background: rgba(0,102,204,0.08); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; border: none;">done</code>, and <code style="font-family: var(--font-mono); background: rgba(0,102,204,0.08); padding: 0.15em 0.4em; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.9em; border: none;">whoami</code>. The recommended way to use Port Daddy.</p>
