commit d5ee1cd3f7db609077aa0a2ffa850732907a9477
Author: Erich Owens <erich.owens@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Mar 10 22:06:48 2026 -0700

    fix(website-v2): font unity, true-black dark theme, GIFs above fold
    
    Typography:
    - Load Inter + JetBrains Mono from Google Fonts (preconnect, not @import)
    - Strip font-mono from all non-code elements: section labels, badges,
      card titles, agent monograms, CTA taglines (15+ instances fixed)
    - Mono now reserved exclusively for: code blocks, terminals, CLI
      commands, version numbers, nav brand name
    
    Dark theme:
    - bg-base #0a0a0a, bg-surface #111 (true black, no navy tint)
    - code-bg #0d1117 (GitHub dark)
    - Neutral text secondaries instead of navy-tinted
    
    Hero:
    - Replace three-panel toggle with direct GIF showcase
    - Add 7-segment rainbow bar above headline (matches v1 style)
    - Remove PortDaddyMark character panel entirely
    - Tab buttons use sans-serif

